Details.Case_Title: Ahmed Omer Khan - VS - FBR & others
Details.Case_Description: Petitioner, being the owner of property in Mall of Islamabad under the banner of Bahria Town, is aggrieved of auction notice dated 22.08.2025 published in Daily Jang. Petitioner further seeks directions to the FBR and CIR to restrain them from attaching or taking any coercive action against the said property.
